<div class="intro">
    <p>Based on official Chinese sources as well as intensive interviews with Hong Kong residents formerly employed in mainland factories, Andrew Walder&#39;s neo-traditional image of communist society in China will be of interest not only to those concerned with China and other communist countries, but also to students of industrial relations and comparative social science.</p>    <p>Winner, 1987 ...</p><p><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="j a_show_full">(展开全部)</a></p></div>
